This repository contains bash scripts!

Refer: https://www.macs.hw.ac.uk/~hwloidl/Courses/LinuxIntro/x945.html
Refer for color and text improve : https://misc.flogisoft.com/bash/tip_colors_and_formatting


1.typeset  -- to make variable local inside function
typeset -i x #interger

2.declare
declare -l lstr="ManoJ" #automatically convert into lowercase variable
-r for readonly

3.read a b -- first goes into a and rest in b

4.seq 1 5  -- prints 1 2 3 4 5

5.{1..5}  -- prints 1 2 3 4 5

6.var=$(function_name)  -- to capture function output

7.export -f function_name  -- to export function

8.|&  -- it will send both stdout and stderr to next command
